HEADWORD: Phaneroglossal
<hw>Phan`er*o*glos"sal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>fanero`s</grk> evident + <grk>glw`ssa</grk> tongue.]</ety>
